        {
            "title": "海關連破西灣河兩私煙倉 檢110萬支私煙 無業內地漢被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/df3c8e3e264e471672903e18a987e350/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031222435149018.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港海關今日（12日）在西灣河一帶展開反私煙巡邏，其間於興民街截查一名47歲男子，在其攜紅白藍袋內搜出2600支私煙。海關隨即將他拘捕，並押返附近一唐樓單位調查，檢獲80萬支私煙，其後再於西灣河街一唐樓劏房單位作跟進調查，檢獲約30萬支私煙。行動中，海關共檢獲約110萬支私煙，市值約500萬元，應課稅值約360萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p>被捕男子為內地人，持雙程證來港，報稱無業。海關指，涉案人士為減低風險，將私煙分散儲存於唐樓單位及劏房單位內，相信行動已搗破兩個供應港島區的私煙儲存及分銷中心。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133819/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關拘捕一名持雙程證的47歲內地男子。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6cf625217f2840856011ea7a44427401/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_222139080.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關拘捕一名持雙程證的47歲內地男子。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133820/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關拘捕一名持雙程證的47歲內地男子。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/38ec53e1dc6ece2a2e36961e3a753112/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_222132628.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關拘捕一名持雙程證的47歲內地男子。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133821/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"西灣河劏房單位私煙儲存倉庫。海關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c7ff11dc5f461bfbe7f8e554208994b/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_220023239.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        西灣河劏房單位私煙儲存倉庫。海關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133822/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"西灣河劏房單位私煙儲存倉庫。海關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/261a1c4cb0fe9dfeb8d339badc646a20/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_220021427.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        西灣河劏房單位私煙儲存倉庫。海關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133823/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"興民街唐樓單位私煙儲存倉庫。海關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76a05ce569320a68d0361695312ff830/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_215943259.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        興民街唐樓單位私煙儲存倉庫。海關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133824/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"興民街唐樓單位私煙儲存倉庫。海關圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/54ac3c6fe528f7f7a72e31973de4486c/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_215941563.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        興民街唐樓單位私煙儲存倉庫。海關圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057808/即時-港聞-海關連破西灣河兩私煙倉-檢110萬支私煙-無業內地漢被捕",
